# Summary
This documentation details the Salesforce Marketing Cloud (Event Streaming) integration with Amplitude, covering setup requirements in both platforms, configuration steps for event and user property forwarding, and explaining how to create Data Extensions and Event Definitions in SFMC to properly receive Amplitude data.

